  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schirach?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schirach was charged in the conspiracy, count one, as were all the defendants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was also charged on count four, which is crimes against humanity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I might tell you how I concluded that case, because I think it's rather dramatic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In making the presentation-- [CLEARS THROAT] in making and preparing for the presentation, one of the documents we had was a translation of a speech he made in Vienna [CLEARS THROAT] to a number of youth leaders from other countries, semi-fascist youth organizations.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the end of it, he said-- and of course, in German-- 'If I am charged with having sent thousands upon thousands of Jews into the ghettos of the East, I consider it a contribution to civilization.' And after I had put in all the other evidence we had, I said, your honors, I'd like to conclude by a statement, which was not only delivered by the defendant von Schirach before youth in Vienna, but which was printed in the word for word, the next day.",
      "word_count": 87
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, I read that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, I mean, I quoted that thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- you could-- and I just said, thank you, and moved away from the podium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a rather striking way to end that presentation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think the-- the-- each of the presentations I made did not take longer than an hour and a half.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think we'd agreed in advance, and that the tribunal had more or less said-- well, as matter of fact, Commander Albrecht, who presented the case against Goering, got sat on by the court very heavily for making colorful remarks that were not necessary, in order to get the evidence in.",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
